The paper also proposes a new architecture for object recognition, which involves the use of machine learning algorithms, indicating that it could also belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses recurrent neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-category.
